communicated by:
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[Because of the persistence of the Ebola virus outbreak in Guinea, President Conde on Sat 6 Jun 2015 extended until the end of June 2015 a health emergency (declared in March 2015). See, from 7 Jun 2015: Guinea extends Ebola emergency measures http://www.ndtv.com/world-news/guinea-extends-ebola-emergency-measures-769386. - Mod.JW]

[This is just one example of why it is so difficult for West Africa to see its way to the end of this Ebola outbreak.

A map of Guinea showing Fria prefecture may be accessed at http://www.worldandcitymaps.com/africa/guinea/. A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map of Guinea can be accessed at https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=3416971,45. - Mod.LK]

